  "comments": "<p><strong>Curiosity</strong><br>(1) <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer ugc\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ef%C3%ADgie_da_Rep%C3%BAblica\"><i>Effigy of the Republic</i></a><br><br>(2) <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer ugc\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Red-and-green_macaw\"><i>Macaw (Arara chloroptera)</i></a><br>---<br><strong>Notes</strong><br><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/5eb1d428e8152.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/5eb1d428e8152.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><br><i>more...</i> <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer ugc\" href=\"https://en.numista.com/numisdoc/brazil-179.html\">Federative Republic of <strong>Brazil</strong></a> and <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer ugc\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brazilian_real\">Real (R$)</a><br>---<br><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/5eb22e2b1e400.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/5eb22e2b1e400.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><br><i><strong>Important:</strong> Date is frozen on 2010 (release of the new banknote series)</i><br>---<br><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/5eb23d9c95edb.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/5eb23d9c95edb.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><br><i>Tactile mark for the visually impaired</i><br>---<br><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/5eb23db14461f.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/5eb23db14461f.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><br><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/5eb23dc20226b.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/5eb23dc20226b.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><br><i>Specimen note sample</i><br><br>UV activity:<br><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/64a040ce32769.png\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/64a040ce32769.png\" alt=\"\"></a><br><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/64a040e4e6c75.png\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/64a040e4e6c75.png\" alt=\"\"></a><br>© gyoschak</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Denomination “10” printed in colour-changing ink, changes colour from emerald green to turquoise when note is tilted:</p><p><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/6688d5b998c70.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/6688d5b998c70.jpg\"></a><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/6688d5bca055b.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/6688d5bca055b.jpg\"></a></p><p>© Kiet Tran</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>There is a security thread present on this banknote, it is only visible under a backlight, inscription “10 REAIS” repeated throughout:\\</p><p><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/6688d60e1caf2.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/6688d60e1caf2.jpg\"></a></p><p>© Kiet Tran</p>",
